      "instruction": "<p>Once everything is nearly ready, boil half a kettle</p><p>Add your<strong> blanched peas</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
